{% doc %}
  @prompt
    A modern SaaS-style hero section UI design for a Thai signage and printing company website. Left side: clean white space with a large bold headline in Thai and English mix, a gradient CTA button (cyan to indigo to lavender), and three small stat counters below a thin divider line (customers, projects, satisfaction score). Right side: a horizontal auto-scrolling collage belt of frosted glass product cards. Cards float on a soft gradient background. Two card sizes ‚Äî tall single cards (portrait) and stacked half-height card pairs ‚Äî arranged in alternating columns. Each card has a large centered emoji icon and a small label underneath. Cards have white semi-transparent background with subtle border and soft drop shadow. Left and right edges of the belt fade to transparent using gradient masks. Background: very soft pastel gradient from mint-cyan (
    #ECFEFF) on the left transitioning through cool periwinkle (
    #EEF2FF) to soft lavender (
    #F5F3FF) on the right. Three subtle radial glow overlays ‚Äî cyan glow at left center, purple glow at top right, sky-blue glow at bottom center. Typography: Google Sans Display for headings. Clean, minimal, lots of white space. UI style: glassmorphism cards, soft shadows, rounded corners (radius ~20px), no harsh borders. Light and airy. Modern B2B e-commerce aesthetic. Desktop layout. 16:9 ratio. Color palette: 
